# Instance-only code — one convention across the tree.
# Every hoster of this repo keeps their custom dashboard code here.
# `(custom)` uses Next.js route groups so URLs don't include the prefix
# (e.g. `app/(custom)/todos/page.tsx` serves at `/todos`).
app/(custom)/
components/custom/
lib/custom/
config/custom-nav.json
